{"tid":1325323,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"突發！做咩啫你 林卓廷篤𣁽可恥 ！","createTime":"2019-07-17T00:07:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T03:52:13.000Z","uid":188721,"like":39,"dislike":479,"uniUserReply":66,"replies":[{"pid":"cf61e05b87cf949d0b5498727cef5f8f6730dbd4","tid":1325323,"uid":188721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T00:07:15.000Z","msg":"［民主黨又賣香港］ 繼昨晚散水成功後，林卓廷今日又落到沙田打算愚弄市民、呼籲散水，還說助理已經影到人手持一袋鐵通，馬上被街坊直斥︰「你威脅我地啊？」「哦！你喺度篤魁！」，這個月來香港人叫得最響的口號「不割蓆、不篤魁」，現在民主黨演繹出另一個版本，「不退場，就篤魁」，泛民支持者又準備點樣兜？<br />\n<br />\n前一晚商場引清兵入關，民主黨說幫你追究責任；今日商場熄冷氣、擺空城，民主黨又跑出來影相篤灰，你還想等民主黨幫你追究？忘記這30年來他們怎樣追究六四屠城責任了嗎？<br />\n<br />\n萬幸，林卓廷現場已經被香港人鬧到退埋一邊，默默地當起一位「無名警察」，維持治安。<br />\n<br />\n#藍屍page <br />\n#分化post<br />\n#林卓廷你分化呀<br />\n#販民五毛全面進場<br />\n#水喉匠<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/327814021474483/posts/336108110645074?s=685319890&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F327814021474483%2Fposts%2F336108110645074%3Fs%3D685319890%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=Xx1rX%2BBWBBKZa4OSQyufSVYPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=78444321\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/327814021474483/posts/336108110645074?s=685319890&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"dacbe09efb3b7d8f31c23e075c29840c447814aa","tid":1325323,"uid":188721,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T00:07:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cd4c2e3fd2eb4224abcf70a421fcbcb798fc7cf3","tid":1325323,"uid":188721,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T00:07:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0274ca662d5bebd02f4734e453f1d05ca998a084","tid":1325323,"uid":188721,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T00:07:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b387b43b580574b71b0becf84b85b0a3e6e19174","tid":1325323,"uid":188721,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T00:08:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"226130ddcf51e3c1c43a6bfce4cf7a87e792ff9c","tid":1325323,"uid":188721,"like":0,