&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F327814021474483%2Fposts%2F336108110645074%3Fs%3D685319890%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=Xx1rX%2BBWBBKZa4OSQyufSVYPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=78444321\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/327814021474483/posts/336108110645074?s=685319890&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T01:06:55.000Z","msg":"我覺得佢真心想大家好，驚有人嫁禍，共產黨咩都做得出。唔好俾機會人入。大家冷靜D先，敵人係㭍婆婆，新城市攪一日好啦，留番D力之後用。"},{"pid":"5ee5d5576297907e1bb81aa9b8b4f07ce505dd92","tid":1325323,"uid":49525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T01:08:55.000Z","msg":"遊行無用，勇武無用，連儂牆無用，民意開始逆轉，開始攰，好想死，仲唔散係弱智，仲唔衝係嘥氣，條例已經死亡，警察已經內鬨<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1320298\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1320298</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"44f13c1d68ce7b672cda7bbf86d5f84a92d0f9dc","tid":1325323,"uid":69891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T01:09:04.000Z","msg":"趠走記者<br />\n趕走議員<br />\n趕走社工<br />\n總之相同信念<br />\n但開聲有唔同表達嘅人都成敵人吧⋯⋯"},{"pid":"778867d7d3f000bd4fe5cbf1399b228f8967b606","tid":1325323,"uid":215755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T01:10:22.000Z","msg":"請善用起底功能"},{"pid":"1c76124fa1f5620cd46287a19091ee79dc9e6ed2","tid":1325323,"uid":205376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T01:11:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">又到凌晨 三毛又出動喇!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1310545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1310545</a></span></span><br />\n<br />\n又黎喇!"},{"pid":"8f4d4f317869811c125fa4f5d82f631526144816","tid":1325323,"uid":264400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a460af0f89302a36c67740de9c761b4ccf4f5979","tid":1325323,"uid":76078,"like":21,"dislike":4,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T00:19:43.000Z","msg":"好心d所謂泛民議員啦 受咗人工30年<br />\n一事冇成 都重唔改下思維<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\